flowchart TD
  I0[Issued invoice exists - from Invoicing]
  R0[Receivable created - base amount from issued snapshot]
  W0[Worklist prioritization - overdue, aging, outstanding]
  F0[Follow-up updates - owner, notes, next action, expected date]
  S0[Settlement effect applied - allocation reduces outstanding]
  P0{Outstanding now}
  C0[Collected or Closed - outstanding equals zero]
  O0[Open or Partial - outstanding above zero]

  I0 --> R0 --> W0 --> F0
  F0 --> S0 --> P0
  P0 -->|Above zero| O0 --> W0
  P0 -->|Equals zero| C0

  subgraph Guards[Guardrails]
    G1[Overdue is computed - due date vs today and outstanding above zero]
    G2[Notes and expected date do not change financial truth]
    G3[No collected without settlement effect]
  end

  W0 -.-> G1
  F0 -.-> G2
  C0 -.-> G3
